<text top="1032" left="342" width="486" height="11" font="2">This record contains the original text of speeches delivered in English and interpretations of speeches</text>
<text top="1047" left="342" width="486" height="11" font="2">delivered in the other languages. The final text will be printed in the <i>Official Records of the Security</i></text>
